  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Railguns, Bombardment, Area-of-Ef=
fect
  and Ion<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>What began as a conflict over the transfer of
  consciousness from flesh to machines escalated into a war which has a
  thousand worlds. The Core and the Arm have exhausted the resources of who=
le
  galactic sectors in their struggle for total domination. Both sides now
  crippled beyond repair, the remnants of their armies continue to battle in
  new regions of space, their hatred fueled by over six hundred years of to=
tal
  war.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>This is a fight to the death. For each side, the only
  acceptable outcome is the complete elimination of the other.<o:p></o:p></=
p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Core have one consciousness, but several sub-rou=
tines
  to handle mundane affairs. Therefore communication is through a proxy
  program. No known image of the consciousness exists.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Though once human, The Core now despise all individu=
alized
  &quot;non-patterned&quot; entities. Their hated rivals, the Arm, are to be
  eliminated on sight.</p>
